        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4094858775" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10032206057755148518">My sister had to read this book in her final year of school. I found it lying in her school bag and started to read it. I soon discovered I loved it. I didn&apos;t have time to finish it sadly, so I bought it online and read it. Just recently I reread it and was weeping at the end all over again. This has to be one of the best books I have ever read and that is why I gave this book five stars.</span>
  <span id="freeText10032206057755148518" style="display:none">My sister had to read this book in her final year of school. I found it lying in her school bag and started to read it. I soon discovered I loved it. I didn't have time to finish it sadly, so I bought it online and read it. Just recently I reread it and was weeping at the end all over again. This has to be one of the best books I have ever read and that is why I gave this book five stars.</span>
